scorporate culture robecosam – we are sustainability investing founded in  robecosam is an investment specialist focused exclusively on sustainability investing to this end we offer a comprehensive palette of products including inhouse asset management sustainability indices corporate sustainability assessments active ownership and engagement and customized portfolio benchmarking solutions   our asset management capabilities accommodate institutional asset owners and financial intermediaries and cover a range of investment products in public equities which integrate environmental social and governance esg factors into the investment process all of our investment strategies and products are designed to make a measurable environmental or societal impact impact investing sustainability insights the st century utility   country sustainability trump to derail the us   article country esg trends in turkey a country going astray   article obesity getting to the heart of the matter   article trump’s energy policy needs renewal   interview avoiding unpleasant surprises   scandinavian trio tops overall sustainability ranking esg risks and opportunities in the textile sector   engage the trend of the world as we know it   interview sustainable water  years of protecting the worlds liquid assets   interview longtermism index impossible engaging to mitigate risks in the soy supply chain   engage water and me us water challenges in flint and beyond   foresight more insights prevention is key click below to read more interesting healthy living facts or order a pdf version of our healthy living article healthy living impact investing video watch robecosam’s head of si research  development and member of executive committee dr daniel wild explain how impact investing can work for core equity strategies read more  newsletter corporate sustainability initiated in  our corporate sustainability assessment csa is an annual assessment of companies’ sustainability practices our approach is unique in that it is based on information provided by the companies directly through the online questionnaire based on a rigorous and rulesbased methodology the csa forms the research backbone of the globally recognized dow jones sustainability indices   we also use the insights derived from the csa in our entire range of asset management products and services our sustainability services offering allows companies experts and practitioners to evaluate their sustainability performance against that of their peers latest press releases robecosam expands its client relations team      jun  robeco and robecosam announce new organizational setup and a more focused client relations approach in switzerland      jun   robecosam collaboration agreement will create a regional environmental social and governance esg index in latin america   feb   robeco teams up with robecosam to manage the optimized equity index strategy with an esg approach for france state reserve fund frr jan   robecosam publishes the annual sustainability yearbook  jan   more news  media important legal information follow us on sustainability investing  robecosam english  deutsch the sustainability yearbook  djsi annual review  the  results of the annual dow jones sustainability indices djsi review have been announced by robecosam and sp dow jones indices impact investing shape the future with impact investing scandinavian trio tops overall sustainability ranking sustainability research research topicscorporate sustainability assessmentcountry sustainability rankingsmart esgfinancial materiality libraryforesightengageinsight  flashstudiesinterviewbrochuresregistration newsletterthe sustainability yearbookwebcastsrobecosam voices focus themesimpact investingwaterclimate changehealthy living strategies  services strategies  servicesfundsasset managementindicessustainability servicesgovernance  active ownershipexclusions about us about robecosamabout robecosam about usmission and visionfacts  figuresexecutive